longBusinessSummary: JSE Limited operates as a securities exchange in South Africa. It offers capital market, post-trade, and information services, as well as listing, trading, and issuer services. The company also provides market services in the areas of equities and bonds, as well as equity, bond, interest rate, commodity, and currency derivatives markets. It also offers post trade services, including clearing, risk management, and settlement services for the equity, bonds, and derivatives markets. The company was founded in 1887 and is based in Johannesburg, South Africa.
